rd%2C%20the%20European%20Union's%20climate%20change%20monitoring%20service%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20the%20last%2010%20months%20ranked%20as%20the%20world's%20hottest%20on%20record%2C%20compared%20with%20the%20corresponding%20month%20in%20previous%20years%2C%20the%20EU's%20Copernicus%20Climate%20Change%20Service%20(C3S)%20said%20in%20a%20monthly%20bulletin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2012%20months%20ending%20with%20March%20also%20ranked%20as%20the%20planet's%20hottest%20ever%20recorded%2012-month%20period%2C%20C3S%20said.%20From%20April%202023%20to%20March%202024%2C%20the%20global%20average%20temperature%20was%201.58%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20the%20average%20in%20the%201850-1900%20pre-industrial%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20long-term%20trend%20with%20exceptional%20records%20that%20has%20us%20very%20concerned%2C%26quot%3B%20C3S%20Deputy%20Director%20Samantha%20Burgess%20told%20Reuters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20records%20like%20this%20-%20month%20in%2C%20month%20out%20-%20really%20shows%20us%20that%20our%20climate%20is%20changing%2C%20is%20changing%20rapidly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fin-secret-test-to-cool-earth-us-scientists-send-sunlight-back-to-space-5379532%5C%22%3EIn%20Secret%20Test%20To%20Cool%20Earth%2C%20US%20Scientists%20Send%20Sunlight%20Back%20To%20Space%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EC3S'%20dataset%20goes%20back%20to%201940%2C%20which%20the%20scientists%20cross-checked%20with%20other%20data%20to%20confirm%20that%20last%20month%20was%20the%20hottest%20March%20since%20the%20pre-industrial%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%202023%20was%20the%20planet's%20hottest%20year%20in%20global%20records%20going%20back%20to%201850.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20has%20witnessed%20extreme%20weather%20and%20exceptional%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClimate%20change-dr