gain%20general%20intelligence%2C%20outsmart%20humans%20by%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712638553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F13%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1710296131-0532.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-says-ai-will-gain-general-intelligence-outsmart-humans-by-2025-124040900177_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20you%20define%20AGI%20(artificial%20general%20intelligence)%20as%20smarter%20than%20the%20smartest%20human%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20probably%20next%20year%2C%20within%20two%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-says-ai-will-gain-general-intelligence-outsmart-humans-by-2025-124040900177_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-says-ai-will-gain-general-intelligence-outsmart-humans-by-2025-124040900177_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Felon-musk-says-ai-will-gain-general-intelligence-outsmart-humans-by-2025-124040900177_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tesla%20EV%20Entry%20In%20India%20Will%20Be%20%26quot%3BNatural%20Progression%26quot%3B%3A%20Elon%20Musk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20said%20that%20India%2C%20like%20every%20other%20country%2C%20should%20have%20electric%20car%20and%20it%20will%20be%20a%20natural%20progression%20for%20his%20company%20to%20provide%20Tesla%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20now%20the%20most%20populous%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20based%20on%20population.%20India%20should%20have%20electric%20cars%20just%20like%20every%20other%20country%20has%20electric%20cars.%20It's%20a%20natural%20progression%20to%20provide%20Tesla%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20X%20Spaces%20session%20with%20Nicolai%20Tangen%2C%20the%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20at%20Norges%20Bank%20Investment%20Management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20CEO%20said%20in%20the%20future%20%26quot%3Ball%20vehicles%20will%20go%20electric%20and%20it%20is%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20lately%20intensified%20its%20efforts%20to%20bolster%20its%20presence%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20and%20is%20actively%20scouting%20for%20a%20suitable%20location%20to%20set%20up%20a%20state-of-the-art%20manufacturing%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20sources%2C%20the%20state%20governments%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat%20have%20extended%20lucrative%20land%20offers%20to%20Tesla%20Inc.%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20manufacturing%20plant%2C%20signalling%20a%20major%20stride%20in%20India's%20electric%20mobility%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20proposed%20plant%2C%20will%20have%20an%20estimated%20investment%20between%20USD%202%20billion%20to%20USD%203%20billion%2C%20and%20will%20aim%20to%20cater%20both%20domestic%20and%20international%20markets%20for%20Tesla's%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20India's%20new%20EV%20policy%2C%20where%20incentives%20have%20been%20provided%20for%20setting%20up%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20India.%20As%20a%20global%20EV%20manufacturer%2C%20Tesla%20plans%20to%20establish%20a%20robust%20manufacturing%20presence%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20government's%20EV%20scheme%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20position%20India%20as%20a%20preferred%20manufacturing%20destination%20for%20EVs%20equipped%20with%20cutting-edge%20technology%2C%20several%20key%20objectives%20are%20outlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20include%20attracting%20investments%20from%20reputable%20global%20EV%20manufacturers%2C%20fostering%20the%20adoption%20of%20advanced%20EV%20technology%20among%20Indian%20consumers%2C%20and%20bolstering%20the%20country's%20Make%20in%20India%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20has%20asked%20for%20a%20minimum%20investment%20threshold%20of%20Rs%204150%20crore%20(USD%20500%20million)%20and%20encouraging%20manufacturers%20to%20achieve%20significant%20levels%20of%20domestic%20value%20addition%20(DVA)%2C%20the%20government%20mandates%20that%20by%20the%20third%20year%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20manufacturing%20unit%2C%20at%20least%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20parts%20used%20to%20make%20the%20vehicles%20should%20be%20sourced%20domestically.%20This%20localization%20level%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20to%2050%20per%20cent%20by%20the%20fifth%20year%20of%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20vehicles%20valued%20at%20USD%2035%2C000%20or%20more%2C%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20customs%20duty%20will%20be%20imposed%20for%20five%20years%20if%20the%20manufacturer%20builds%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20India%20within%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20total%20number%20of%20EVs%20allowed%20for%20import%20under%20the%20policy%20will%20be%20limited%20based%20on%20the%20investment%20made.%20or%20of%20a%20maximum%20he%20value%20of%20Rs%206484%20crore%2C%20whichever%20is%20lower.%20If%20the%20investment%20exceeds%20USD%20800%20million%2C%20a%20maximum%20of%2040%2C000%20EVs%20can%20be%20imported%2C%20with%20no%20more%20than%208%2C000%20per%20year%2C%20as%20per%20the%20policy.%20Unused%20import%20limits%20can%20be%20carried%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20investment%20plans%2C%20Tesla%20intends%20to%20send%20a%20team%20of%20experts%20to%20scout%20for%20suitable%20locations%20across%20India%20for%20the%20proposed%20manufacturing%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%20reported%2C%20citing%20an%20Indian%20official%2C%20that%20the%20government%20would%20formally%20invite%20applications%20for%20the%20EV%20tariff%20reduction%20scheme%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20month%2C%20under%20which%20eligible%20companies%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20import%20up%20to%208%2C000%20vehicles%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20Chief%20Executive%20Elon%20Musk%20in%20June%20last%20year%20said%20that%20he%20was%20planning%20to%20visit%20India%20in%202024%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20confident%20that%20the%20electric%20carmaker%20will%20be%20in%20India%20and%20will%20do%20so%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20humanly%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20told%20reporters%20in%20New%20York%2C%20following%20a%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20was%20then%20on%20a%20historic%20four-day%20State%20visit%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20had%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi%20invited%20him%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20PM%20Modi%20for%20his%20support%20and%20hopefully%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20announce%20something%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Piyush%20Goyal%20had%20visited%20Tesla's%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20California's%20Fremont%20and%20said%20that%20the%20US%20electric%20car%20maker%20is%20on%20its%20way%20to%20double%20its%20components%20imports%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20had%20stressed%20that%20he%20was%20proud%20to%20see%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20auto%20component%20suppliers%20from%20India%20in%20the%20Tesla%20EV%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712638380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffrr9q5p_elon-musk-reuters_6