racy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sierra%20Leone%20Declares%20National%20Emergency%20Over%20Drug%20Made%20From%20Human%20Bones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20psychoactive%20drug%20crafted%20from%20human%20bones%20is%20leaving%20addicts%20in%20the%20West%20African%20country%20of%20Sierra%20Leone%20digging%20up%20graves%20in%20order%20to%20get%20their%20fix.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20haunting%20menace%20has%20forced%20Sierra%20Leone%20to%20declare%20a%20national%20emergency.%20Police%20officers%20in%20Freetown%20are%20guarding%20cemeteries%20to%20thwart%20the%20disturbing%20practice%20of%20exhuming%20skeletons%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BZombie%26quot%3B%20drug%20production.%20Notably%2C%20the%20drug%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bkush%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20made%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20toxic%20substances%2C%20with%20one%20of%20its%20main%20ingredients%20being%20ground-up%20human%20bone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narcotic%20first%20emerged%20in%20the%20West%20African%20country%20around%20six%20years%20ago.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68742694%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20induces%20a%20hypnotic%20high%20which%20can%20last%20several%20hours.%20The%20drug%20has%20become%20a%20widespread%20problem%20and%20dealers%20have%20reportedly%20turned%20into%20grave%20robbers%2C%20breaking%20into%20thousands%20of%20tombs%20to%20steal%20skeletons%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20country%20is%20currently%20faced%20with%20an%20existential%20threat%20due%20to%20the%20ravaging%20impact%20of%20drugs%20and%20substance%20abuse%2C%20particularly%20the%20devastating%20synthetic%20drug%20Kush%2C%26quot%3B%20Sierra%20Leone%20President%20Julius%20Maada%20Bio%20said%2C%20per%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bio%20added%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bescalating%20fatalities%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20drug%20users.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20he%20has%20set%20up%20a%20task%20force%20to%20eradicate%20the%20drug.%20This%20means%20there%20will%20be%20centres%20in%20every%20district%20%26quot%3Badequately%20staffed%20by%20trained%20professionals%20to%20offer%20care%20and%20support%20to%20people%20with%20drug%20addiction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20officials%20have%20also%20been%20urged%20to%20break%20the%20drug%20supply%20chain%20by%20%26quot%3Binvestigations%2C%20arrests%20and%20prosecutions%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Freetown%20is%20home%20to%20the%20country's%20only%20functioning%20drug%20rehabilitation%20centre.%20The%20100-bed%20facility%20was%20hurriedly%20set%20up%20in%20an%20army%20training%20centre%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Experts%20have%20reportedly%20described%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20holding%20centre%20than%20a%20rehab%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20its%20lack%20of%20adequate%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froyal-bank-of-canada-fires-cfo-over-undisclosed-close-relationship-with-another-employee-5403350%5C%22%3ERoyal%20Bank%20Of%20Canada%20Fires%20CFO%20Over%20''Undisclosed%20Close%20Relationship''%20With%20Another%20Employee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Abdul%20Jalloh%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Sierra%20Leone%20Psychiatric%20Hospital%2C%20said%20that%20the%20President's%20emergency%20declaration%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20step%26quot%3B%20and%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%20in%20addressing%20drug%20use%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20official%20death%20toll%20linked%20to%20%26quot%3Bkush%26quot%3B%20abuse%2C%20but%20one%20doctor%20from%20Freetown%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20hundreds%20of%20young%20men%20had%20died%20fro