t%20in%20Singapore%20that%20can%20be%20given%20to%20male%20offenders%20who%20are%20below%2050.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%2026-year-old%20Indonesian%20man%20was%20sentenced%20to%2018%20months%20in%20prison%20and%20nine%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%20in%20Singapore%20for%20illegally%20entering%20the%20island%20nation%20by%20swimming%2C%20local%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingaporean%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.channelnewsasia.com%2Fsingapore%2Frepeat-immigration-offender-jailed-caned-swim-back-singapore-abandon-sampan-4250161%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChannel%20News%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20identified%20the%20man%20by%20only%20one%20name%20%E2%80%94%20Brick%20%E2%80%94%20and%20reported%20that%20he%20approached%20Singapore%20on%20a%20small%20boat%20called%20a%20sampan%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boat%20set%20off%20from%20Batam%2C%20an%20Indonesian%20island%20about%20eight%20miles%20south%20of%20Singapore%2C%20and%20Brick%20later%20jumped%20into%20the%20water%20and%20swam%20to%20shore%2C%20CNA%20reported%2C%20citing%20details%20given%20during%20his%20sentencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Brick's%20fifth%20illegal%20entry%20into%20Singapore%20since%202017%2C%20with%20his%20previous%20offenses%20landing%20him%20a%20total%20of%2025%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%20and%2050%20months%20in%20prison%2C%20per%20CNA.%20Given%20his%20latest%20sentence%2C%20the%20total%20rises%20to%2034%20cane%20strokes%20and%2068%20months%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20immigration%20authorities%20arrested%20Brick%20in%20March%20and%20said%20in%20court%20that%20he%20didn't%20have%20travel%20documents%20to%20show%20that%20he%20entered%20the%20country%20legally%2C%20per%20CNA.%20That%20means%20he%20spent%20about%20nine%20months%20living%20illegally%20in%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20court%2C%20Brick%20asked%20in%20Indonesian%20for%20leniency%20because%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bworking%20for%20my%20family%20and%20my%20mother%20currently%20is%20ill%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20presiding%20judge%20said%20Brick's%20repeated%20offenses%20required%20a%20tougher%20sentence%2C%20CNA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Immigration%20%26amp%3B%20Checkpoints%20Authority%20of%20Singapore%2C%20which%20prosecuted%20Brick's%20case%2C%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20Indonesian%20Embassy%20in%20Singapore%20also%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20similar%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudicial%20caning%20is%20a%20form%20of%20corporal%20punishment%20in%20Singapore%20that%20can%20be%20given%20to%20criminal%20offenders%20who%20are%20male%20and%20under%20the%20age%20of%2050.%20The%20penalty%20is%20often%20paired%20with%20a%20prison%20sentence%20and%20carried%20out%20by%20trained%20staff%20with%20a%20special%20rattan%20cane%20about%20four%20feet%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaff%20are%20trained%20to%20strike%20the%20bare%20buttocks%20of%20the%20offender%2C%20and%20the%20lashes%20are%20said%20to%20be%20extremely%20painful%20and%20sometimes%20leave%20scars.%20An%20offender%20can%20receive%20a%20maximum%20of%2024%20strokes%20per%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20caning%20in%20Singapore%20has%20been%20controversial%2C%20drawing%20international%20attention%20in%201994%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F1994%2F06%2F27%2Fus%2Fteen-ager-caned-in-singapore-tells-of-the-blood-and-the-scars.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E19-year-old%20US%20citizen%20Michael%20Fay%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20given%20six%20strokes%20of%20the%20cane%20for%20vandalism.%20Fay%20later%20said%20local%20police%20coerced%20him%20into%20a%20confession%20that%20he%20spray-painted%20cars%2C%20a%20claim%20that%20the%20Singapore%20government%20has%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefenders%20of%20caning%20say%20it%20acts%20both%20as%20a%20deterrent%20and%20a%20means%20to%20make%20offenders%20think%20twice%2