-more-celebs-attend-amar-singh-chamkila-special-screening-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F109150920.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDhoni%20Still%20Taking%20Those%20Calls%26quot%3B%3A%20Ruturaj%20Explains%20CSK%20Leadership%20Setup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20returned%20to%20winning%20ways%20with%20a%20victory%20over%20KKR%2C%20captain%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20who%20finished%20the%20match%20with%2067%2C%20became%20%26quot%3Bnostalgic%26quot%3B%20as%20MS%20Dhoni%20was%20also%20with%20him%20when%20he%20hit%20his%20first%20IPL%20fifty.%20Riding%20on%20Tushar%20Deshpande%2C%20Mustafizur%20Rahman%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja's%20brilliance%20followed%20by%20Gaikwad%20and%20Shivam%20Dube's%20fine%20knocks%2C%20helped%20CSK%20register%20a%207-wicket%20victory%20against%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20their%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20match%20here%20at%20MA%20Chidambaram%20Stadium%20on%20Monday.%20CSK%20continued%20domination%20at%20their%20fortress%20as%20they%20cruised%20home%20without%20really%20breaking%20a%20sweat%2C%20ending%20KKR's%20unbeaten%20run%20in%20this%20edition%20of%20the%20IPL.%20Chennai%20skipper%20Gaikwad%20remained%20unbeaten%20at%2067%20as%20he%20slammed%20the%20winning%20runs%20for%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20said%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20maiden%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20half-century%20Dhoni%20was%20there%20with%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bfinish%20the%20match.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLittle%20nostalgic%20for%20me.%20During%20my%20first%20IPL%20fifty%2C%20a%20similar%20situation%2C%20Mahi%20bhai%20was%20with%20me%20and%20we%20finished%20the%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaikwad%20said%20in%20a%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaikwad%20further%20claimed%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Ajinkya%20Rahane%20due%20to%20injury%2C%20he%20took%20up%20the%20duty%20of%20