nday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20going%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20away%20with%20the%20so-called%20golden%20visa%20scheme%20that%20allows%20access%20to%20residency%20in%20exchange%20for%20investing%20500%2C000%20euros%20in%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20said%20while%20visiting%20an%20area%20near%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Seville.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%2C%20which%20will%20be%20approved%20at%20Tuesday's%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20will%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20fight%20against%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%20investment%26quot%3B%20in%20property%2C%20which%20is%20preventing%20%26quot%3Bmany%20young%20people%20and%20families%26quot%3B%20from%20accessing%20housing%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20--%20which%20was%20introduced%20in%202013%20when%20the%20economy%20was%20struggling%20and%20Spain%20wanted%20to%20attract%20foreign%20capital%20--%20offers%20non-EU%20investors%20a%20three-year%20work%20and%20residency%20permit%20in%20exchange%20for%20investing%20at%20least%20500%2C000%20euros%20(%24542%2C000)%20in%20property%20or%20a%20Spanish%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%2094%20out%20of%20every%20hundred%20visas%20of%20this%20nature%20are%20linked%20to%20property%20investment%20that%20is%20concentrated%20in%20large%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20Barcelona%2C%20Madrid%2C%20Malaga%2C%20and%20Alicante%20in%20the%20south%2C%20Valencia%20in%20the%20east%2C%20and%20Spain's%20Mediterranean%20Balearic%20Islands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20areas%20were%20experiencing%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20tension%20in%20the%20housing%20market%2C%20making%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20those%20living%2C%20working%20and%20paying%20taxes%20there%20to%20find%20decent%20housing%2C%26quot%3B%20Sanchez%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20several%20countries%20in%20southern%20Europe%20that%20set%20up%20similar%20schemes%20during%20the%20financial%20crisis%2C%20have%20tightened%20the%20rules%20or%20dropped%20the%20offer%20altogether%20to%20ease%20their%20respective%20housing%20crises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20Portugal%20ended%20its%20golden%20visa%20programme%20which%20had%20significantly%20pushed%20up%20house%20prices%2C%20and%20late%20last%20month%2C%20Greece%20tightened%20the%20rules%20on%20its%20own%20scheme%2C%20raising%20the%20required%20investment%20to%20as%20much%20as%20800%2C000%20euros.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20visas%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20European%20disgrace.%20You%20can't%20grant%20someone%20a%20residency%20permit%20just%20because%20he's%20a%20millionaire%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Culture%20Minister%20Ernest%20Urtasun%20who%20is%20also%20the%20spokesman%20for%20the%20radical%20leftwing%20Sumar%20party%2C%20part%20of%20Spain's%20Socialist-led%20ruling%20coalition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Brussels%20urged%20member%20states%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20such%20schemes%2C%20saying%20they%20largely%20benefited%20wealthy%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20investors%2C%20and%20warned%20that%20the%20practise%20was%20likely%20to%20facilitate%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712633160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fb9nk8fn_spain-generic_625x300_09_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fspain-to-scrap-golden-visa-scheme-for-foreign-real-estate-investors-5403561%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Spain%20is%20to%20axe%20its%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visa%26quot%3B%20scheme%20under%20which%20foreign%20investors%20get%20residency%20for%20a%20500%2C000-euro-investment%20in%20property%2C%20to%20curb%20the%20speculation%20blighting%20many%20Spanish%20cities%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Pedro%20Sanchez%20said%20on