job%20at%20Google%20is%20two%20pages%20long%20%E2%80%94%20a%20decision%20he%20defends%20today.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fankitvirmani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnkit%20Virmani%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20spent%20five%20years%20in%20consulting%20when%20he%20began%20eyeing%20a%20shift%20to%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20thought%20in%20my%20heart%20that%20I%20wanted%20more%20technical%20depth.%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20things%20rather%20than%20sell%20them%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Virmani%2C%20who%20first%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20from%20India%20to%20pursue%20a%20master's%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20half%20of%202020%2C%20he%20dove%20right%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20wrapping%20up%20a%20day%20at%20his%20full-time%20job%20at%20Deloitte%2C%20Virmani%20would%20spend%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20practicing%20coding%20every%20night%2C%20and%20another%20two%20hours%20reading%20up%20about%20the%20industry.%20He%20also%20began%20spending%20time%20with%20people%20in%20the%20field%2C%20asking%20them%20about%20real-time%20scenarios%20and%20what%20challenges%20they%20face%20in%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20answers%20from%20them.%20I%20wanted%20their%20thought%20process%20%E2%80%94how%20do%20they%20navigate%20through%20these%20complex%20challenges%20at%20scale%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20didn't%20pay%20off%20right%20away.%20He%20was%20rejected%20by%20Microsoft%20and%20Amazon%20at%20different%20stages%20of%20their%20application%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20after%20deciding%20to%20switch%20careers%2C%20he%20landed%20a%20role%20as%20a%20data%20and%20machine%20learning%20specialist%20at%20Google's%20Seattle%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20he%20used%20to%20apply%20for%20his%20job%20at%20Google%2C%20which%20pays%20more%20than%20%24300%2C000%20a%20year.%20BI%20has%20verified%20his%20employment%20and%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ankit%20Virmani%20Resume%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660ee1a416bde8d4ead5be90%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221424%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20two-page%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20Virmani%20used%20to%20apply%20to%20Google%20in%202020.%3Cp%3EAnkit%20Virmani%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESacrificing%20the%20'one-page%20only'%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20rule%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20four%20years%20later%2C%20Virmani%20said%20he%20would%20make%20some%20formatting%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is%20giving%20importance%20to%20everything%20equally%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20don't%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20a%20gradient%20of%20importance%2C%20like%20executive%20summary%20on%20top%2C%20achievements%20so%20far%2C%20and%20then%20I%20would%20go%20to%20professional%20experience%2C%20education%2C%20and%20technical%20skills.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20more%20insight%20into%20what%20employers%20like%20Google%20appreciate%2C%20Virmani%20said%20he%20would%20keep%20several%20things%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20the%20length%20of%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESacrificing%20the%20%26quot%3Bone-page%20only%26quot%3B%20rule%20to%20improve%20readability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVirmani%20broke%20the%20%26quot%3Bone-page%20only%26quot%3B%20rule%20and%20prioritized%20having%20an%20uncluttered%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20very%20neatly%20structured%20sections%20and%20high-level%20themes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20about%20using%20subheadings%20like%20%26quot%3Bdata%20architecture%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcloud%20strategy.%26quot%3B%20His%20manager%20at%20Google%20later%20told%20him%20that%20style%20helped%20them%20pick%20up%20on%20his%20responsibilities%20without%20having%20to%20decipher%20the%20lines%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHighlighting%20team%20effort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Virmani%20said%20some%20people%20overly%20highlight%20individual%20contributions%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20that%20way%2C%20at%20least%20in%20my%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20always%20teamwork.%26quot%3B%20That's%20why%20he%20focused%20parts%20of%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20on%20his%20teams'%20accomplishments.%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20highly%2C%20highly%20appreciates%20honesty%20and%20humility.%20That's%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20we%20know%20that%20nothing%20great%20gets%20achieved%20by%20an%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaving%20some%20details%20for%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Virmani%20said%20he%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20over-explain%20his%20past%20projects%20so%20that%20he%20could%20build%20curiosity%20and%20have%20a%20good%20conversation%20during%20the%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20everything%20in%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20you'll%20run%20out%20of%20points%20to%20talk%20about%20in%20the%20interview.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EVirmani%20is%20not%20alone%20in%20choosing%20to%20sacrifice%20%26quot%3Btypical%26quot%3B%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20decisions.%20For%20Shola%20West%2C%20that%20came%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20breaking%20the%20%26quot%3Bno%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20gap%26quot%3B%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20is%20part%20of%20a%20growing%20group%20of%20Gen%20Zs%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-rewriting-rulebook-jobs-resume-gaps-career-breaks-work-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edestigmatize%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20period%20of%20unemployment%20between%20jobs%20or%20between%20education%20and%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20previou