-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20his%20days%20of%20struggle%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20back%20in%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202019.%20Karthik%2C%20currently%20playing%20for%20RCB%2C%20has%20set%20the%20IPL%20on%20fire%20with%20his%20skill%20as%20a%20finisher.%20In%20the%20tournament%20so%20far%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20his%20last%20IPL%20ever%2C%20Karthik%20has%20made%2090%20runs%20in%20four%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2045.00%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20173.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20247%20IPL%20matches%2C%20Karthik%20has%20made%204%2C606%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2026.02%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20133%2C%20having%20scored%2020%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20is%2097*.%20He%20is%20the%2010th-highest%20run-getter%20in%20the%20tournament's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20stint%20with%20Delhi%20Capitals%20till%202010%2C%20the%20right-handed%20batter%20had%20stints%20with%20Kings%20XI%20Punjab%20(now%20Punjab%20Kings%2C%202011)%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(2012-13)%2C%20Delhi%20again%20in%202014%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%20(2015%2C%202022-present)%2C%20Gujarat%20Lions%20(2016-17)%2C%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(2018-21).%20He%20won%20the%202013%20IPL%20title%20with%20MI%2C%20which%20remains%20his%20only%20IPL%20title%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%2C%20who%20won%20the%202013%20season%20with%20MI%2C%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E's%20YouTube%20channel%20that%20his%20regret%20was%20not%20wanting%20to%20be%20retained%20by%20the%20Blue%20and%20Gold%20franchise%20after%20a%20brilliant%202013%20season.%20Staying%20with%20MI%20would%20have%20helped%20him%20grow%20into%20an%20even%20better%20player.%20His%20another%20regret%20was%20not%20being%20able%20to%20represent%20his%20home%20state%20with%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20had%20to%20actually%20ask%20me%20one%20of%20my%20regrets%20in%20my%20cricketing%20career%20in%20respect%20to%20IPL%2C%20it%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20get%20retained%20in%202013.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20rewind%20that%20whole%20thing%20and%20go%20back%2C%20and%20that%20is%20when%20I%20think%20sometimes%2C%20as%20a%20young%20player%2C%20you%20need%20someone%20as%20a%20life%20coach%2C%20if%20I%20had%20had%20Abishek%20Nayar%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20I%20know%20he%20would%20have%20said%20play%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Karthik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20have%20too%20many%20regrets%20in%20life.%20I%20am%20not%20that%20kind%20of%20a%20person%2C%20but%20if%20I%20have%20two%20regrets%20in%20my%20cricketing%20career%20in%20terms%20of%20IPL%2C%20one%20would%20be%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20chose%20not%20to%20get%20retained%20because%20I%20thought%20MI%20was%20a%20team%20that%20could%20have%20really%20helped%20me%20grow%20and%20become%20an%20even%20better%20player.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20two%20would%20be%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20obviously%2C%20I%20could%20not%20represent%20CSK%20so%20far.%20But%20that%20I%20understand%2C%20though%20it%20is%20a%20regret%20because%20I%20could%20not%20play.%20I%20mean%2C%20coming%20from%20Chennai%2C%20I%20played%20all%20my%20cricket%20there%2C%20and%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20yellow%20jersey%2C%20but%20I%20always%20respect%20them%20because%20they%20genuinely%20try%20every%20year%20to%20try%20and%20get%20me%20in%20the%20auction%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wicketkeeper-batter%20said%20that%20he%20had%20an%20option%20to%20stay%20with%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20but%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20stay%20despite%20the%20infrastructure%20present%2C%20the%20star%20power%20and%20the%20leadership%20of%20captain-coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ricky%20Ponting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F348-ricky-ponting-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERicky%20Ponting%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20then.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20the%20Ambani%20family%20as%20well%2C%20who%20owned%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20be%20retained%2C%20and%20I%20declined%20it%20because%20I%20thought%20if%20I%20went%20into%20the%20auction%2C%20you%20know%2C%20a%20typical%20young%20boy%20who%20wanted%20to%20obviously%20chance%20his%20time%20in%20the%20auction%2C%20and%20I%20went%20inside%20and%20I%20became%20part%20of%20the%20auction.%20I%20just%20felt%20if%20I%20had%20been%20part%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20at%20that%20stage%2C%20I%20would%20have%20grown%20a%20lot%20more%20as%20a%20player.%20The%20kind%20of%20infrastructure%20they%20had%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20team%20that%20they%20built%2C%20and%20being%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20was%20led%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20%5BRicky%5D%20Ponting%20was%20a%20coach%2C%20and%20the%20owners%20were%20brilliant%20with%20me%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20really%20good%20relationship%20with%20Akash%20%5BAmbani%5D%2C%20Anant%20%5BAmbani%5D%2C%20and%2C%20to%20a%20small%20extent%2C%20even%20Nita%20%5BAmbani%5D%20bhabhi.%20So%20I%20had%20a%20good%20relationship%2C%20and%20you%20know%2C%20I%20just%20felt%20that%20if%20I%20had%20been%20part%20of%20that%20team%2C%20it%20would%20have%20helped%20me%20grow%20as%20a%20cricketer%20and%20as%20a%20person%2C%20and%20hence%2C%20when%20I%20look%20back%20at%20it%2C%20a%20decade%20has%20passed%20since%20I%20just%20felt%20I%20missed%20an%20opportunity%20there%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202013%20season%2C%20Karthik%20scored%20510%20runs%20in%2019%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2028.33%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20over%20124%2C%20with%20two%20fifties.%20His%20best%20score%20was%2086.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarthik%2C%20who%20captained%20KKR%20from%202018-20%2C%20admitted%20that%20there%20were%20some%20%26quot%3Btough%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20spinner%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20who%20had%20to%20stay%20benched%20after%20taking%20just%20four%20wickets%20in%20nine%20games%20in%20the%202019%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wicketkeeper-batter%20revealed%20that%20the%20spinner%20was%20not%20doing%20as%20well%20as%20he%20is%20right%20now%20and%20he%20had%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhonest%26quot%3B%20with%20Kuldeep.%20He%20expressed%20happiness%20at%20spinner's%20progress%20since%20then%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20has%20become%20a%20better%20bowler%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bworld-beater%26quot%3B.%20He%20expressed%20hope%20that%20Kuldeep%2C%20now%20a%20part%20of%20Delhi%20Capitals%20since%202022%2C%20is%20able%20to%20understand%20what%20Dinesh%20wanted%20to%20convey%20to%20him%20back%20then%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20personal%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeading%20a%20franchise%20is%20altogether%20a%20different%20job.%20There%20are%20many%20other%20cultures%2C%20and%20you%20will%20find%20it%20challenging%20to%20deal%20with%20other%20individuals.%20You%20can%20be%20very%20honest%20with%20them.%20As%20a%20leader%2C%20you%20will%20lose%20out%20on%20certain%20friendships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20my%20time%20as%20KKR%20captain%2C%20Kuldeep%20(Yadav)%20was%20not%20doing%20as%20well%20as%20he%20is%20right%20now.%20There%20were%20tough%20conversations%20with%20him%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20he%20would%20have%20appreciated%20me%20at%20that%20stage.%20I%20had%20to%20be%20tough%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20hard%20time%20for%20Kuldeep.%20I%20