l%2C%20Canada%2C%20office%20workers%20spilled%20out%20of%20skyscrapers%20to%20snap%20pictures%20with%20their%20eclipse%20glasses%20held%20to%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20heart%20was%20beating%20really%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%2026-year-old%20Erica%20Park.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20of%20totality%20was%20115%20miles%20(185%20kilometers)%20wide%20and%20home%20to%20nearly%2032%20million%20Americans%2C%20with%20an%20additional%20150%20million%20living%20less%20than%20200%20miles%20from%20the%20strip%2C%20according%20to%20NASA%2C%20which%20ran%20a%20live%20webcast%20throughout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESchool%20closures%2C%20mass%20weddings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHotels%20and%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20prime%20viewing%20locations%20were%20booked%20solid%20for%20months%20in%20advance%20across%20states%20including%20Texas%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20Ohio%20and%20Maine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ingram%2C%20Texas%2C%20at%20the%20Stonehenge%20II%20park%20--%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20prehistoric%20monument%20in%20England%20--%20eclipse%20watchers%20gathered%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20undeterred%20by%20overcast%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeni%20Lyn%20Hunter%2C%2057%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20Charles%20Guillory%2C%2060%2C%20had%20traveled%20from%20Floresville%2C%20Texas.%20The%20couple%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3Bpagans%26quot%3B%20and%20wore%20Merlin%20hats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20me%20because%20I%20have%20stage%20four%20cancer%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20giving%20up%2C%20this%20is%20a%20rebirth%20of%20the%20Sun%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunter%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20Russellville%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20more%20than%20300%20couples%20reportedly%20exchanged%20vows%20at%20%26quot%3BA%20Total%20Eclipse%20of%20the%20Heart%26quot%3B%20mass%20wedding%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%