ial%20acts%20taken%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Smith%20said%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bradical%26quot%3B%20claim%20has%20no%20historical%20precedent%20and%20risks%20allowing%20future%20presidents%20to%20get%20away%20with%20crimes%20ranging%20from%20bribery%20to%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20bedrock%20principle%20of%20our%20constitutional%20order%20is%20that%20no%20person%20is%20above%20the%20law%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%20wrote%20in%20this%20week's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.supremecourt.gov%2FDocketPDF%2F23%2F23-939%2F306999%2F20240408191803801_United%2520States%2520v.%2520Trump%2520final%2520for%2520filing.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiling%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20set%20to%20rule%20on%20Trump's%20immunity%20claim%20on%20April%2025%2C%20the%20last%20day%20of%20oral%20arguments%20for%20the%20top%20court's%20current%20term.%20Trump%20previously%20appealed%20a%20lower%20court's%20unanimous%20ruling%20that%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fappeals-court-ruling-trump-immunity-jack-smith-election-interference-case-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20could%20be%20charged%20with%20the%20counts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20take%20up%20the%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court's%20decision%20to%20hear%20Trump's%20appeal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmuse.insider.com%2Fstory%2F66148eb4c0360126a30f971e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificantly%20delayed%20the%20start%20of%20a%20potential%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20initially%20set%20to%20begin%20in%20March.%20It%20was%20a%20major%20win%20for%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20delay%20his%20myriad%20legal%20troubles%20as%20long%20as%20possible%20before%20the%20November%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegal%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20month%20that%20they%20think%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus