e're%20exploring%20the%20nature%20of%20humanity%20and%20our%20deep%2C%20deep%20flaws%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20things%20that%20we%20will%20do%20for%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20on-set%20photo%20of%20Critical%20Role's%20Liam%20O'Brien.%20He's%20wearing%20a%20dark%20green%20Cardigan%20and%20a%20striped%2C%20button-down%20shirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660fa1843f923f7dab04eaf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiam%20O'Brien%20gets%20to%20unleash%20his%20inner%20chaos%20gremlin%20in%20the%20game%20master%20seat.%3Cp%3ECritical%20Role%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20last%20installment%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCrimson%20Mirror%26quot%3B%20series%20scheduled%20to%20air%20on%20April%2025%2C%20O'Brien%20said%20things%20are%20about%20to%20get%20intense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20prefer%20complicated%20narratively%20satisfying%20endings%20to%20a%20neat%20little%20happy%20ending%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Brien%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20into%20this%20game%20with%20a%20mindset%20of%20how%20I%20would%20run%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20characters%20surprised%20me%2C%20and%20the%20story%20we%20ended%20up%20telling%20is%20not%20where%20I%20saw%20things%20going%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20all%20the%20better%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20long%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpenser%20Starke%20and%20Rowan%20Hall%2C%20the%20lead%20designers%20and%20cowriters%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BCandela%20Obscura%26quot%3B%20game%20at%20Darrington%20Press%2C%20told%20me%20they%20worked%20on%20the%20rulebook%20for%2011%20months%2C%20writing%20the%20lore%20and%20ironing%20out%20the%20game%20mechanics%20with%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20playtesting.%20Since%20August%2C%20multiple%20game%20masters%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mercer%2C%20Starke%