front%20of%20Lake%20Champlain%20to%20watch%20the%20event%20unfold%20over%20the%20Adirondack%20Mountains.%3Cp%3EEllyn%20Lapointe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20helped%20make%20my%20first%20eclipse%20experience%20great%20was%20the%20advice%20I%20received%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mreclipse.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFred%20Espanak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20NASA%20astrophysicist%20and%20avid%20eclipse%20chaser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspanak%20has%20been%20to%2030%20total%20solar%20eclipses%20and%20has%20seen%20one%20on%20all%20seven%20continents%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Antarctica.%20He's%20seen%20so%20many%20that%20he%20earned%20the%20nickname%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Eclipse%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20he%20has%20his%20eclipse-watching%20strategy%20down%20to%20a%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20April%208%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20my%20first%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20experience.%20Here%20are%20the%20tips%20he%20gave%20me%20that%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20most%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGet%20to%20the%20path%20of%20totality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMillions%20of%20Americans%20traveled%20to%20the%20path%20of%20totality%20for%20Monday's%20eclipse%2C%20and%20Espanak%20would%20say%20they%20had%20the%20right%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20a%20partial%20eclipse%20might%20be%20interesting%2C%20a%20total%20eclipse%20is%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Total%20solar%20eclipse%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661465511caec1275a6df96c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20photo%20of%20totality%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20sun's%20corona%20glowing%20white%20around%20the%20perimeter%20of%20the%20moon's%20shadow.%3Cp%3EEllyn%20Lapointe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20spoke%20with%20Espanak%20in%20February%2C%20I%20called%20from%20my%20apartment%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20New%20York.%20New%20York%20City%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20path%20of%20totality%2C%20but%20would%20see%20the%20moon%20cover%20about%2090%25%20of%20the%20sun%20during%20the%20eclipse.%20Espanak%20encouraged%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20city%20and%20travel%20to%20the%20path%20of%20totality%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20train%20to%20Burlington%2C%20Vermont%2C%20to%20watch%20the%20event.%20And%20it%20was%20totally%20worth%20the%20seven-hour%20trip.%20In%20Burlington%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20see%20three%20minutes%20and%2015%20seconds%20of%20totality%2C%20which%20was%20unlike%20anything%20I%20had%20ever%20seen%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKeep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20weather%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20can%20make%20or%20break%20your%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20experience.%20Cloudy%20skies%20or%20precipitation%20in%20the%20forecast%20can%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20see%20and%20photograph%20the%20event%20%E2%80%94%20some%20eclipse%20chasers%20in%20New%20York%20learned%20this%20the%20hard%20way.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20it's%20important%20to%20keep%20your%20eye%20on%20the%20weather%20forecast%20during%20the%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20eclipse%2C%20Espenak%20said%2C%20and%20be%20prepared%20to%20change%20your%20viewing%20location%20to%20find%20clearer%20skies%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20be%20willing%20to%20change%20your%20plans%20a%20day%20or%20two%20before%20the%20eclipse%20based%20on%20the%20weather%20forecasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Espenak%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20grassy%20field%20with%20a%20crowd%20of%20people%20lounging%20under%20a%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661470ed1caec1275a6dfc6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaterfront%20Park%20in%20Burlington%2C%20VT%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20the%20eclipse%20began.%20A%20few%20clouds%20rolled%20in%20later%20on%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20obstruct%20my%20view%20of%20the%20eclipse.%3Cp%3EEllyn%20Lapointe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVermont's%20weather%20in%20April%20can%20be%20unpredictable%20%E2%80%94%20ranging%20from%20snow%2C%20rain%2C%20and%20high%20winds%20to%20sun%20and%20blue%20skies.%20I%20checked%20the%20weather%20every%20day%20in%20the%20week%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20eclipse.%20Luckily%20for%20me%2C%20Burlington%20was%20sunny%20and%20warm%20for%20eclipse%20day%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20make%20any%20last-minute%20changes%20to%20my%20viewing%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEspanak's%20tips%20made%20my%20first%20total%20eclipse%20experience%20unforgettable.%20And%20now%2C%20I'll%20be%20prepared%20for%20the%20next%20one%20in%20the%20US%20in%202044.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feclipse-chasers-advice-made-my-solar-eclipse-experience-breathtaking-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712618670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66144cda3f923f7dab05acd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feclipse-chasers-advice-made-my-solar-eclipse-experience-breathtaking-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20eclipse%20chaster%20who%20has%20been%20to%2030%20total%20solar%20eclipses%20gave%20me%20his%20best%20advice%20for%20making%20the%20most%20of%20my%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellyn%20Lapointe)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A64%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feclipse-chasers-advice-made-my-solar-eclipse-experience-breathtaking-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%