%20suggestions%20can%20help%20you%20work%20towards%20that%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3E1.%20Cut%20your%20living%20expenses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20able%20to%20downsize%20your%20living%20expenses%2C%20it%20could%20allow%20you%20to%20save%20more.%20While%20this%20may%20mean%20moving%20from%20one%20home%20to%20another%2C%20it%20could%20also%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20slashing%20your%20spending%20and%20revisiting%20your%20budget%20to%20see%20where%20you%20can%20cut%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20retiree%20and%20blogger%20A%20Purple%20Life%20(who%20is%20anonymous%20online)%20cut%20her%20costs%20by%20moving%20from%20New%20York%20City%20to%20Seattle.%20Retiring%20just%20five%20years%20after%20she%20started%20saving%2C%20the%20move%20helped%20her%20progress.%20%26quot%3BI%20cut%20my%20living%20costs%20in%20half%20just%20by%20moving%20out%20of%20Manhattan%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20cutting%20her%20expenses%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20retire%20quickly.%20Doing%20something%20similar%20to%20lower%20your%20expenses%20might%20help%20your%20retirement%20journey%2C%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%5D%5C%22%3E2.%20Pay%20off%20any%20debt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20it's%20possible%20for%20you%20to%20pay%20off%20debt%2C%20it%20will%20benefit%20your%20retirement%20goals%20twofold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20be%20able%20to%20save%20more%20money%20each%20month%20with%20one%20less%20responsibility.%20Freeing%20up%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20each%20month%20means%20you'll%20have%20more%20cash%20to%20put%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Esavings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20invest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20there's%20a%20long-term%20benefit.%20Going%20into%20retirement%20without%20debt%20can%20help%20to%20keep%20costs%20low%20and%20stretch%20t