r%20violating%20the%20Election%20Integrity%20Act%20of%202021%20in%20the%20first%20episode%20of%20the%20season.%20During%20the%20trial%2C%20the%20district%20attorney%2C%20Earl%20Mack%20(Greg%20Kinnear)%2C%20calls%20character%20witnesses%20to%20testify%20against%20Larry.%20They're%20all%20people%20who%20have%20had%20memorable%20spats%20with%20Larry%20on%20the%20show%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20Mocha%20Joe%20(Saverio%20Guerra)%2C%20Irma%20(Tracey%20Ullman)%2C%20and%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20mirrors%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-worst-series-finales-of-all-time-seinfeld-girls-dexter-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSeinfeld%26quot%3B%20series%20finale%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20that%20episode%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Finale%2C%26quot%3B%20past%20characters%20from%20throughout%20the%20show's%20nine%20seasons%20returned%20as%20character%20witnesses%20after%20Jerry%20(Jerry%20Seinfeld)%2C%20George%20(Jason%20Alexander)%2C%20Elaine%20(Julia%20Louis-Dreyfus)%2C%20and%20Kramer%20(Michael%20Richards)%20were%20arrested%20and%20put%20on%20trial%20for%20violating%20a%20local%20Good%20Samaritan%20law%20in%20a%20small%20Massachusetts%20town%20when%20they%20didn't%20intervene%20to%20help%20a%20man%20getting%20car-jacked.%20Much%20like%20Larry%20being%20confronted%20by%20the%20many%20people%20who%20hate%20him%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BSeinfeld%26quot%3B%20also%20crew%20faced%20ghosts%20from%20their%20past%20dredging%20up%20their%20bad%20behavior%20during%20their%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20twist%20is%20how%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flarry-david-almost-didnt-make-another-curb-your-enthusiasm-season-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCurb%20Your%20Enthusiasm%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20ending%20differs.%20%26quot%3BSeinfeld%26quot%3B%20ends%20with%20the%20four%20leads%20being%20found%20guilty%20and%20sentenced%20t