r%20launch%20in%202021%2C%20they%20have%20sold%20over%2011%2C500%20devices%20and%20have%20earned%20a%20revenue%20of%20Rs%205.5%20crore%20in%20FY%202023-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20bagged%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crore%20in%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20Season%203%20from%20Peyush%20Bansal%2C%20valuing%20their%20company%20at%20Rs%20250%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20exactly%20is%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20and%20what%20makes%20their%20patented%20product%20unique%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMade%20in%20India%20for%20the%20world%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kanishka%20and%20Raj%20founded%20WeHear%20in%202021%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-03-14-at-5.34.08-PM-1712583368-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346836%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKanishka%20and%20Raj%20founded%20WeHear%20in%202021%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanishka%20recalls%20being%20fascinated%20by%20audio%20and%20electronics.%20He%20participated%20in%20many%20robotics%20competitions%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20often%20came%20across%20brilliant%20innovations%2C%20hoping%20to%20make%20one%20himself%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20about%2018%20to%2019%20pairs%20of%20earphones%20as%20I%20love%20listening%20to%20music.%20When%20I%20read%20about%20the%20bone%20conduction%20technology%20used%20in%20the%20US%20Army%2C%20I%20wondered%20about%20the%20other%20use%20cases%20for%20it.%20I%20started%20researching%20and%20developed%20a%20prototype%20of%20a%20hearing%20aid%20using%20this%20technology%20in%202017%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kanishka%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ahmedabad%20resident%20then%20spoke%20about%20this%20idea%20with%20his%20co-founder%20Raj%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20joined%20him%20to%20build%20the%20device.%20They%20were%20incubated%20at%20the%20Gujarat%20University%20Startup%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Council%20(GUSEC)%2C%20where%20they%20received%20funding%20and%20support%20to%20start%20their%20research%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20tweaks%2C%20when%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20prototype%2C%20they%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bahera%20Munga%20Shala%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20a%20school%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297383%2Fmumbai-ojas-maheshwari-with-hearing-impairment-tops-iit-jee-advanced-shares-strategy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing-impaired%3C%2Fa%3E%20children%20to%20test%20their%20device.%20The%20moment%20that%20the%20duo%20dearly%20cherish%2C%20is%20the%20first%20ti