ells%2C%20and%20using%20treated%20wastewater%20as%20a%20genuine%20resource.%20Here%20we%E2%80%99ll%20discuss%20what%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20help!)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20issues%20of%20state%20capacity%20and%20the%20need%20to%20recalibrate%20water%20policy%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20residents%20can%20do%20to%20mitigate%20the%20water%20scarcity%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296593%2Fbengaluru-floods-zenrainman-s-vishwanath-expert-shares-water-logging-solutions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%20Vishwanath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20civil%20engineer%20and%20urban%20planner%20with%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20water%20and%20sanitation%20sector%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20consume%20less%20water%2C%20recycle%20greywater%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20to%20minimise%20my%20demand%2C%20then%20there%20is%20some%20amount%20of%20water%20which%20I%20can%20save%20within%20my%20whole%20zone.%20And%20the%20administration%20can%20transfer%20some%20of%20my%20zone%E2%80%99s%20water%20to%20another%20which%20is%20facing%20scarcity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20living%20in%20the%20affected%20area%2C%20especially%20in%20apartment%20complexes%20with%2020%20units%20or%20more%20(that%20are%20mandated%20to%20have%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plant)%2C%20Vishwanath%20believes%20that%20if%20they%20make%20sure%20that%20their%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants%20are%20running%20well%2C%20then%20they%20can%20fulfil%20all%20their%20non-potable%20water%20requirements%20from%20those%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20residents%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20well%2C%20their%20borewells%20will%20have%20water.%20If%20the%20community%20works%20around%20the%20lakes%20in%20their%20neighbourhood%2C%20comes%20together%2C%20and%20makes%20sure%20that%20the%20lake%20is%20cleaned%20up%20and%20de-silted%20along%20with%20the%20State%2C%20then%20these%20water%20bodies%20will%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20aquifer.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20excess%20water%20from%20their%20STPs%20that%20are%20well%20treated%20can%20be%20led%20into%20these%20lakes%20so%20that%20it%20recharges%20the%20aquifers.%20I%20believe%20these%20are%20all%20the%20steps%20that%20citizens%20have%20to%20take%20to%20protect%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20water%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recommends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20what%20steps%20has%20he%20taken%20in%20his%20own%20home%20to%20reduce%20water%20consumption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%20being%20mindful%20of%20the%20amount%20of%20water%20you%20consume%2C%20you%20can%20deploy%20technologies%20like%20aerators%20on%20your%20taps%20or%20shower%20heads.%20You%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20water%20you%20collect%20after%20cleaning%20your%20dishes%20is%20used%20to%20water%20your%20plants%20or%20the%20garden%20that%20you%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20case%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20all%20the%20greywater%20is%20recycled.%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20collect%20the%20wastewater%20from%20my%20washing%20machine%20and%20half-bucket%20bath%20water.%20I%20use%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F230971%2Fnagaland-small-biz-entrepreneur-woman-organic-soaps-oils-skincare-personal-care-eco-friendly-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-friendly%20soaps%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20detergents%20which%20do%20not%20have%20phosphates%20and%20phthalates.%20This%20means%20that%20the%20wastewater%20from%20bathing%20or%20washing%20clothes%20can%20be%20used%20for%20swabbing%20the%20floor%2C%20watering%20the%20terrace%20garden%2C%20and%20cleaning%20the%20car.%20I%20have%20a%20dry%20compost%20toilet%20which%20requires%20no%20water%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20may%20seem%20a%20bit%20extreme%20to%20some%20but%20it%20has%20worked%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F92434%2Fa-r-shivakumar-rainwater-harvesting-bengaluru-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erainwater%20harvesting%3C%2Fa%3E%20systems%20that%20are%20operating%20optimally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20last%20rains%20in%20the%20city%20were%20in%20November%2C%20our%201%2C000-litre%20rain%20barrel%20still%20has%20enough%20water%20for%20our%20drinking%20and%20cooking%20needs%20till%20June.%20I%20have%20taken%20away%20plants%20which%20would%20have%20otherwise%20grown%20and%20left%20the%20garden%20to%20be%20dry%20so%20that%20when%20the%20rains%20come%2C%20I%20can%20restart%20my%20garden.%20Right%20now%2C%20I%20only%20have%20drought-tolerant%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20use%20less%20energy%20(electricity).%20The%20less%20energy%20I%20use%2C%20the%20more%20water%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20in%20some%20dam%20or%20thermal%20power%20plant.%20You%20have%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20energy%20you%20use%20and%20about%20the%20food%20you%20eat%20so%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20waste%20it.%20These%20are%20some%20of%20the%20steps%20I%20have%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FyyRNm-mFn7g%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3