0DNA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20seen%20my%20father%20and%20grandfathers%20grow%20crops.%20But%20like%20them%2C%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20grow%20traditional%20crops%20like%20mustard%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20grams.%20I%20wanted%20to%20try%20new%20technologies.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20crops%20that%20required%20less%20water%20to%20grow%20in%20our%20dry%20region%20of%20Rajasthan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fdates-3-1712555430-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346770%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMukesh%20says%20Barhi%20and%20Khuneji%20varieties%20give%20high%20yields%20in%20low%20maintenance%20and%20have%20lower%20mortality%20rates%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20as%20a%20commando%2C%20Mukesh%20had%20already%20started%20preparing%20himself%20to%20take%20up%20farming.%20But%20in%202018%2C%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20to%20his%20village%20