hat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20they%20say%20challenges%20are%20a%20part%20of%20any%20business.%20What%20sets%20the%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%20apart%2C%20however%2C%20is%20its%20recipe%20for%20dealing%20with%20adversity.%20The%20women%20and%20children%20have%20never%20shied%20away%20from%20steering%20the%20legacy%20forward%20when%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20cousins%20laugh%20over%20childhood%20anecdotes%2C%20stories%20of%20taking%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20family%20legacy%20and%20nostalgic%20memories%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%20%E2%80%94%20the%20dairy%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20just%20a%20family%20business%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20loved%20member%20that%20has%20had%20its%20own%20seat%20at%20the%20family%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChildhood%20summers%20and%20hot%20piping%20%3Cem%3Ejalebis%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20family%20behind%20the%20legacy%20of%20Parsi%20Dairy%20Farm%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fparsi-dairy-farm-1711120124-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345654%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%